		</g>
	</svg>
</span>
<span class="site-logo-slot site-logo-slot--full" aria-hidden="true">
	<svg class="site-logo-mark" viewBox="0 0 168 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
		<g fill="currentColor">
			<rect x="1" y="5" width="26" height="16" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" />
			<rect x="5" y="9" width="4" height="8" rx="0.5" />
